msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: source/authorization_services/topics/getting-started/hello-world/deploy.adoc:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "There are a plenty of things you can do now to test this application. For example, you can change the default policy by clicking the Authorization tab for the client, then `Policies` tab, then click on `Default Policy` in the list to allow you to change it as follows:\n"
msgstr ""

#.  The default value is $evaluation.grant(),
#.  let's see what happens when we change it to $evaluation.deny()
#. type: Plain text
#: source/authorization_services/topics/getting-started/hello-world/deploy.adoc:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "```js\n"
"$evaluation.deny();\n"
msgstr ""

#.  now you can use the RPT to access protected resources on the resource server
#. type: Plain text
#: source/authorization_services/topics/getting-started/hello-world/deploy.adoc:99
#: source/authorization_services/topics/service/client-api.adoc:82
#: source/authorization_services/topics/service/client-api.adoc:109
#, no-wrap
msgid "```\n"
